00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.520
Four of the most important things every woman needs in a relationship.

00:00:04.521 --> 00:00:08.521
Achieve all of these and you'll be able to keep any high value,

00:00:08.522 --> 00:00:10.901
marriage material woman in your life

00:00:10.920 --> 00:00:14.900
number one- whatever woman needs is you to be her security.

00:00:14.960 --> 00:00:18.480
meaning you value her and you put her first,

00:00:18.481 --> 00:00:21.321
She knows that she's the only girl for you,

00:00:21.322 --> 00:00:24.481
you don't entertain any other woman that isn't her.

00:00:24.482 --> 00:00:25.201
Not only that,

00:00:25.202 --> 00:00:28.161
you don't ignore her when you're hanging out with your friends,

00:00:28.162 --> 00:00:29.381
keep her in the loop,

00:00:29.600 --> 00:00:30.960
be her security.

00:00:30.961 --> 00:00:33.161
number two- give her validation

00:00:33.162 --> 00:00:35.921
this means having those hard conversations

00:00:35.922 --> 00:00:38.821
when she ask you where you stand in the relationship.

00:00:38.920 --> 00:00:42.360
take the relationship seriously so she's not questioning you.

00:00:42.361 --> 00:00:44.461
you need to assure her,

00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:49.040
make sure that her emotions are being understood and that she feels seen.

00:00:49.041 --> 00:00:52.101
No. 3- give her enough attention

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:55.200
this could be as simple as writing her a cute note,

00:00:55.201 --> 00:00:58.161
or sending her thoughtful text throughout the day.

00:00:58.162 --> 00:01:01.161
You also need to be affectionate with her,

00:01:01.162 --> 00:01:02.041
give her a hug,

00:01:02.042 --> 00:01:04.021
give her a smooch on the forehead,

00:01:04.040 --> 00:01:06.160
women love that and melt for that.

00:01:06.161 --> 00:01:07.801
And don't forget to compliment her.

00:01:07.802 --> 00:01:09.201
Is she wearing a new outfit?

00:01:09.202 --> 00:01:11.341
is she wearing her hair differently?

00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:14.320
Make sure you notice and compliment her on that.

00:01:14.321 --> 00:01:18.401
that's all any woman wants is to feel seen and complimented 

00:01:18.402 --> 00:01:19.528
praise her 

00:01:19.529 --> 00:01:24.341
No. 4- this should come as a no brainer but you have to, put in the effort

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:26.600
do not avoid having hard,

00:01:26.601 --> 00:01:30.241
vulnerable conversations if she's trying to have them with you

00:01:30.242 --> 00:01:31.741
to understand you better.

00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:34.500
Also make sure you're making enough time for her,

00:01:34.520 --> 00:01:35.820
life gets busy,

00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:38.680
but as long as you're trying to see her,

00:01:38.681 --> 00:01:40.601
that's all any woman wants

00:01:40.602 --> 00:01:42.001
put in the effort to hang out

00:01:42.002 --> 00:01:45.681
