00:01:45.682 --> 00:01:49.921
just put an effort so she knows that you care about her

00:01:49.922 --> 00:01:51.481
that's all any woman wants

00:01:51.482 --> 00:01:52.801
if you put an effort,

00:01:52.802 --> 00:01:54.701
